data.title: Ben Chapman - Autograph in "Creature from the Black Lagoon"
data.meta_description: American actor (1928-2008) best known as playing the Gill-man on land in the 1954 horror film "Creature from the Black Lagoon".  Color movie still photo from the film "Creature from the Black Lagoon", inscribed with a short sentiment and dated in 1997.  Size is 9.9 x 7.9 inches, in excellent condition.
